{
  "page": "Willis Wode",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the Kingsguard, see <a href=\"/index.php/Willis_Fell\" title=\"Willis Fell\">Willis Fell</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Wode\" title=\"House Wode\"><img alt=\"House Wode.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c4/House_Wode.svg/50px-House_Wode.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c4/House_Wode.svg/75px-House_Wode.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/c4/House_Wode.svg/100px-House_Wode.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Willis Wode</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Wode\" title=\"House Wode\"><img alt=\"House Wode.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c4/House_Wode.svg/50px-House_Wode.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c4/House_Wode.svg/75px-House_Wode.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/c4/House_Wode.svg/100px-House_Wode.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Wode\" title=\"House Wode\">House Wode</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Whent\" title=\"House Whent\">House Whent</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">Rivermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">Riverlands</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafwillis_wode.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafwillis_wode.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appendix)</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">Played by</span></th><td>\nRyan McKenna</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">TV series</span></th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>: <a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_Season_1\" title=\"Game of Thrones - Season 1\">Season 1</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Willis Wode</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Wode\" title=\"House Wode\">House Wode</a> in the service of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Whent\" title=\"House Whent\">House Whent</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> He is possibly one of the brothers Wode who are <a href=\"/index.php/Landed_knight\" title=\"Landed knight\">landed knights</a> sworn to <a href=\"/index.php/House_Whent\" title=\"House Whent\">House Whent</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In the television adaptation <i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>, Willis is portrayed by Ryan McKenna.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes_by_Willis\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes by Willis</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Quotes_about_Willis\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes about Willis</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Willis_Wode&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Stiff-necked and stolid,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Willis is an older man<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> whom <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> thinks of as a <a href=\"/index.php/Hedge_knight\" title=\"Hedge knight\">hedge knight</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The black <a href=\"/index.php/Bat\" title=\"Bat\">bat</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Whent\" title=\"House Whent\">House Whent</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a> is embroidered on Willis's surcoat.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> The knight wields a spiked morningstar, and his helmet has a thin slit for his eyes and a long black <a href=\"/index.php/Silk\" title=\"Silk\">silk</a> plume.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Willis_Wode&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Willis_Wode&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>When <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a> takes <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> prisoner at the <a href=\"/index.php/Inn_at_the_crossroads\" title=\"Inn at the crossroads\">inn at the crossroads</a>, Ser Willis is the first of the <a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">rivermen</a> to proclaim his loyalty to <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tully\" title=\"House Tully\">House Tully</a> and aid Catelyn.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Catelyn decides to bring Tyrion to the <a href=\"/index.php/Eyrie\" title=\"Eyrie\">Eyrie</a> instead of <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> When Catelyn's party is attacked by <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_mountain_clans\" title=\"Vale mountain clans\">mountain clansmen</a> on the <a href=\"/index.php/High_road\" title=\"High road\">high road</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Morrec\" title=\"Morrec\">Morrec</a> helps Willis with his armor when <a href=\"/index.php/Marillion\" title=\"Marillion\">Marillion</a> is too frightened to assist. Willis cries out \"<a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a>!\" as he rides against the wildings. Catelyn wishes to bury the dead after the battle, but Willis urges that they continue their journey through the dangerous <a href=\"/index.php/Mountains_of_the_Moon\" title=\"Mountains of the Moon\">Mountains of the Moon</a> instead of delaying.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Willis is the only one of the rivermen to survive the journey to the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_of_Arryn_(valley)\" title=\"Vale of Arryn (valley)\">Vale of Arryn</a>. He and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Cassel\" title=\"Rodrik Cassel\">Rodrik Cassel</a> remain at the <a href=\"/index.php/Bloody_Gate\" title=\"Bloody Gate\">Bloody Gate</a> to have their wounds treated by a <a href=\"/index.php/Septon\" title=\"Septon\">septon</a> while Catelyn continues on with Tyrion to the <a href=\"/index.php/Gates_of_the_Moon\" title=\"Gates of the Moon\">Gates of the Moon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> \n</p><p>Willis and Rodrik continue on to the Eyrie, and Willis chuckles when Tyrion publicly demands a <a href=\"/index.php/Trial_by_combat\" title=\"Trial by combat\">trial by combat</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> His whereabouts after Tyrion leaves the Eyrie<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> are unknown.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Willis_Wode&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>On the journey to resolve the <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Riverrun\" title=\"Siege of Riverrun\">siege of Riverrun</a>, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a> and his host come across the lands once held by the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Wode\" title=\"House Wode\">brothers Wode</a>, two <a href=\"/index.php/Landed_knight\" title=\"Landed knight\">landed knights</a> sworn to <a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a>: it is possible that one of them is Ser Willis. Jaime encounters neither member of the Wode family or their <a href=\"/index.php/Smallfolk\" title=\"Smallfolk\">smallfolk</a> but finds both of their timber keeps burned down, and he hangs several <a href=\"/index.php/Outlaws\" title=\"Outlaws\">outlaws</a> taking shelter in the cellar beneath one of the ruined halls.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_by_Willis\">Quotes by Willis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Willis_Wode&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes by Willis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Willis</b>: Lady Stark, I urge you to press on, with all haste. We drove <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_mountain_clans\" title=\"Vale mountain clans\">them</a> off for the moment, but they will not have gone far.<br />\n</p><p><b>Catelyn</b>: We must bury our dead, Ser Willis. These were brave men. I will not leave them to the <a href=\"/index.php/Crow\" title=\"Crow\">crows</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Shadowcat\" title=\"Shadowcat\">shadowcats</a>.<br />\n</p>\n<b>Willis</b>: This soil is too stony for digging.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Willis and <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_about_Willis\">Quotes about Willis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Willis_Wode&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes about Willis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>He was <a href=\"/index.php/Shella_Whent\" title=\"Shella Whent\">Lady Whent's</a> man, stiff-necked and stolid, and the first to rise to aid <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a> back at <a href=\"/index.php/Inn_at_the_crossroads\" title=\"Inn at the crossroads\">the inn</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Willis_Wode&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Appendix\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiafwillis_wode.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafwillis_wode.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>, Willis Wode.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a hre